<H3> <TI>   Iliescu Receives South Korean Business Group </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU0401184994 Bucharest ROMPRES in English 1751 GMT 4 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU0401184994 </F>
<F P=104>  Bucharest ROMPRES </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <FÊP=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] <LOCATION>Bucharest</LOCATION> ROMPRES 4/1/1994 -- <LOCATION>Romania</LOCATION>'s President 
<PERSON>Ion Iliescu</PERSON> received on <DATE>January 4, 1994</DATE>, a delegation of the 
North [as received] Korean Daewoo group, led by <PERSON>Kim U-chung</PERSON>, 
chairman of the administration board. 
  The <ORGANIZATION>Daewoo</ORGANIZATION> group intends to explore ways for large-scale 
investments in <LOCATION>Romania</LOCATION> in the car-making industry, 
ship-building, refineries, electronics, tourism and the 
financial-banking sector. 
  President <PERSON>Iliescu</PERSON> saluted the interest of South Korean 
businessmen in cooperation actions in <LOCATION>Romania</LOCATION> and told his guest 
about the potentialities of the Romanian economy, the 
opportunities created for foreign investors by the Romanian 
legislation. The Romanian president encouraged the 
representives of the <ORGANIZATION>Daewoo</ORGANIZATION> group to have contacts with Romanian 
businessmen in view of making mutually advantageous transactions. 

</TEXT>

